== Template:Exercise ==

This template creates a purple exercise box for hands-on practice.

=== Usage ===

<pre>
{{Exercise|
Your exercise instructions here.
Can include multiple steps:
# Step one
# Step two
# Step three
}}
</pre>

=== Example ===

{{Exercise|
Try creating a new branch called "feature/hello-world":
# Create and switch to the new branch
# Add a new file called hello.txt
# Commit your changes
# Push the branch to GitHub
}}

